  title `The Slum Areas (Improvement and Clearance) Act, 1956`
  actNumber (96)
  enactmentDate 1956-12-29
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1709`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `गन्दी बस्ती क्षेत्र (सुधार तथा उन्मूलन) अधिनियम, 1956`
